emuInput.TitMainTitle: Members of Herron Hill and Westinghouse swim teams posed during junior high school swimming meet at Allegheny High School
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 22, 1952, pg. 27, reads: "Junior High Champs - Some of the crack group of Junior High School swimmers that participated in the school boy title meet last week at Allegheny High School pose proudly above. Shown in the top picture are members of Herron Hill's and Westinghouse's crack teams... - Harris Photos."
